*slaps roof of costume* this bad boi has 22 pockets in it! 
I'm thrilled to show off this sleeveless coat I made for LARP. It was a magical item I "found" during a heist last game and the item card required it to be made in order to be used. This has been the most fun I've had in years because my entire goal was to create a visual disaster. 
Meet my "Uncomfortably Colorful Patchwork Clothing"
Another delightful thing I made that I've been waiting to share until after LARP. 
I went to the dentist to pick up my night guard and they were like "do you want the mold of your teeth?" Of course I said yes. So from an unpainted 3d mold of my teeth to a nightmare sock puppet meeeeet....Chatterbox. 
I played with the puppet at a Halloween party and then got to watch my friend terrify the town while on my photography shift this past weekend.
My thorned hand was also related to nightmare stuff....don't worry about it. 
.
#LARP #costume #liveactionroleplay #cosplay #elf #puppet
